This project can be compiled and executed on  Linux, Unix, MacOs, Windows systems.

On Linux and MacOs,
--------------------
To compile, write in a terminal: 	make all 
On Windows 10,
--------------------
 Open a terminal in this directory:  Menu of Windows/Visual Studio/x86 Native Tools Command Prompt
write: move Makefile_win32 Makefile
To compile, write: 	nmake all 
Informations about this project are in the file: editor/PluginEditor.cc


Instructions how to install c++ and root on your computer:
 https://www-fourier.ujf-grenoble.fr/~faure/enseignement/c++/cours_c++/cours_1/cours_1.xhtml 
